N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 732.2 - Period covered

State Regulations

Every public utility shall file its annual report on the
basis of the calendar year, and every municipality operating an electric, gas
or steam system on the basis of its fiscal year. Notes
